HEADWORD: Benedictus
<hw>Ben`e*dic"tus</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
blessed. See <er>Benedict</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>The song of
